Fake meatballs displayed at a trade fair of merchants on Alibaba's e-commerce platform Taobao pique visitors' curiosity in Hangzhou, capital of East China's Zhejiang Province on Monday. The domestically developed fake meat products debuted at another Taobao trade fair in September, and now they're on many Chinese dinner tables. Photo: IC 
